OL,3,CAlmost half a million pounds to be
OL,4,Cspent undoing 'yellow brick road'
OL,6,FNorth Somerset Council will spend
OL,7,Falmost half a million pounds to undo
OL,8,Fmost of the "yellow brick road" scheme
OL,9,Falong Clevedon seafront.
OL,11,FThe redesign of the seafront sparked
OL,12,Fcriticism from residents in the town
OL,13,Fwhen parking was removed and replaced
OL,14,Fwith a cycle lane, wiggly lines and a
OL,15,Froad surface compared to the yellow
OL,16,Fbrick road in the Wizard of Oz.
