OL,3,CAlmost half a million pounds to be
OL,4,Cspent undoing 'yellow brick road'
OL,6,FSince then, a review into the
OL,7,Fcontroversial scheme has taken place
OL,8,Fand the council has voted to approve
OL,9,Fspending #425k to reverse most
OL,10,Funpopular aspects of the scheme.
OL,12,FUnder the plans much of the sea-facing
OL,13,Fparking on The Beach will be restored,
OL,14,Fthe wavy lines, two-way cycle lane,
OL,15,Fand most of the yellow buff will be
OL,16,Fremoved.
OL,18,FThe one-way system and 20mph speed
OL,19,Flimit will remain, and there will be a
OL,20,Fsingle contraflow cycle lane installed
OL,21,Finstead.
