OL,3,CAlmost half a million pounds to be
OL,4,Cspent undoing 'yellow brick road'
OL,6,FThe move has been welcomed by people
OL,7,Fin the town affected by the scheme.
OL,9,FCathy Hawkins, a founding member of
OL,10,Fthe "Save Our Seafront" campaign,
OL,11,Fsaid: "It just shows that if you fight
OL,12,Fto change something, it can be
OL,13,Fchanged."
OL,15,FBut she urged councillors to think
OL,16,Fagain about installing a contraflow
OL,17,Fcycle lane. She warned: "Having to
OL,18,Flook both ways both for cars and for
OL,19,Fcyclists coming down the hill quite
OL,20,Ffast is an accident waiting to happen."
