OL,4,Cspent undoing 'yellow brick road'
OL,6,FWork on the seafront could start in
OL,7,Fthe autumn, in order to avoid
OL,8,Fdisrupting the seaside town in the
OL,9,Fsummer, and it could be completed by
OL,10,Fthe end of the year.
